        Standard MML assumptions:
        ===========================
        FX Rates (NZD base):
          USD: 0.60  (1 NZD = 0.60 USD → 1 USD = 1.6667 NZD)
          AUD: 0.90  (1 NZD = 0.90 AUD → 1 AUD = 1.1111 NZD)
          CNY: 4.00  (1 NZD = 4.00 CNY → 1 CNY = 0.2500 NZD)

        Customer Payment Terms:
          Default:       45 days from invoice, snap to 20th
          Harvey Norman: 15th of the month following invoice
          Briscoes:      Last calendar day of month following invoice

        Freight:
          $100 per CBM (sea freight, all-in estimate)
    -->

</odoo>
